name: Prince Khadman
description: I am a fun loving man, jovial, Kind, easy going, lovely and passionate man. I like to have fun, work, travel, Play, and smile. I think of myself as being clever but harmless. My Hobbies include jogging, music, horse riding, traveling, cooking . I am looking for a woman whom I will love, and also the woman that I would be able to spend the rest of my life with.
